Inspired by traditional indie-folk music, Amélie Farren writes her music to reflect a life of whimsical fantasy and glittering fame, with eerie thoughts hidden between the lines. Lyrics:

[Verse 1]
I'm two days into college
And I'm three lectures behind
There's this guy, let's name him Colin
He says he wants to be mine
But it doesn't really sit with me quite right
'Cause he doesn't really like the things I like
And I keep accidentally locking myself out of my dorm in the middle of the night

[Verse 2]
I wake up kinda wired
And I wake up kinda cold
And I wake up kinda tired
But I'll just sleep in when I'm old
See I don't like breaking rules
But don't like doing as I'm told
So I just float around and keep my head down
And hope my life unfolds

[Chorus]
And еverybody's telling me that I'm doing so wеll
I try to trust them, honestly
I find it hard to tell
If I need work or I need rest
I try my best to try my best
I tell myself
I say out loud
It's fine
I'll figure it all out
I tend to forget
I'm still only quite young
In a way this life of mine has only just begun

[Refrain]
I've got time
I've got time

I'm two days into college
With a busy, busy mind
That guy that we named Colin
He's so handsome, he's so kind
My friends tell me I'm crazy
Say I take it way too far
'Cause I told him that it's over
'Cause he doesn't play guitar

[Verse 4]
I'm only two days into college
And my bedroom is a mess
There's just so much that I want to do
That I have not done yet
There's just so much that I want to say
And far too little breath
Oh my mind it runs so far away
It's easy to forget

[Chorus]
That to everybody else it looks like I'm doing so well
I try to see it, honestly
I find it hard to tell
If I've done wrong or I've done right
I need a good night's sleep tonight
They said go out
I said alright
I think I won't
I maybe might
I probably should just take it slow
I'll be all good
But God I know

[Bridge]
The one thing that's important above everything else
Is to learn not to put all this heavy pressure on myself
I try believe it when I say
If it's meant to happen it'll happen anyway
I'll be fine

[Refrain]
I've got time
I've got time

[Outro]
That's where I'm at
To be honest
Just two days
Two days into college

title: THE *NSYNC SCENE from Trolls Band Together! ("Better Place" Credits Sequence) | TROLLS BAND TOGETHER
description:
→ WATCH MORE ← https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=UULFY26xU0-avwTJ6F6TzUZVEw
→ SUBSCRIBE ← https://www.youtube.com/c/PeacockKids?sub_confirmation=1

Trolls Band Together - Available now on Blu-Ray, DVD, and VOD

This holiday season, get ready for an action-packed, all-star, rainbow-colored family reunion like no other as Anna Kendrick and Justin Timberlake return for the new chapter in DreamWorks Animation’s blockbuster musical franchise: Trolls Band Together. 

After two films of true friendship and relentless flirting, Poppy (Anna Kendrick) and Branch (Justin Timberlake) are now officially, finally, a couple (#broppy)! As they grow closer, Poppy discovers that Branch has a secret past. He was once part of her favorite boyband phenomenon, BroZone, with his four brothers: Floyd (Golden Globe nominated electropop sensation Troye Sivan), John Dory (Eric André; Sing 2), Spruce (Grammy winner Daveed Diggs; Hamilton) and Clay (Grammy winner Kid Cudi; Don’t Look Up). BroZone disbanded when Branch was still a baby, as did the family, and Branch hasn’t seen his brothers since.  

But when Branch’s bro Floyd is kidnapped for his musical talents by a pair of nefarious pop-star villains—Velvet (Emmy winner Amy Schumer; Trainwreck) and Veneer (Grammy winner and Tony nominee Andrew Rannells; The Book of Mormon)—Branch and Poppy embark on a harrowing and emotional journey to reunite the other brothers and rescue Floyd from a fate even worse than pop-culture obscurity. 

Featuring Trolls’ signature psychedelic joy-bomb of new and classic pop hits, Trolls Band Together stars a dazzling cast of musical superstars and comedic powerhouses as new franchise characters, including four-time Grammy nominee and Latin Grammy winner Camila Cabello (Cinderella) as Viva; Zosia Mamet (The Flight Attendant) as Crimp; and 12-time Emmy winning drag icon RuPaul Charles as Miss Maxine. 

The returning cast includes Grammy, Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Zooey Deschanel as Bridget; Christopher Mintz-Plasse as Gristle, the Icona Pop duo Aino Jawo and Caroline Hjelt as Satin and Chenille, Grammy winner Anderson .Paak as Prince D, comedian Ron Funches as Cooper, SAG nominee Kunal Nayyar as Guy Diamond and Emmy winning Saturday Night Live legend Kenan Thompson as Tiny Diamond. 

Trolls Band Together is steered by returning director Walt Dohrn and producer Gina Shay, and is co-directed by Tim Heitz (head of story, Trolls World Tour). DreamWorks Animation’s Trolls films—2016’s Trolls and 2020’s Trolls World Tour—have sung and danced their way to record-breaking success, earning an Oscar® nomination for Best Original Song and fueling one of the largest and most beloved entertainment brands in the world.


Join the fun on Peacock Kids where you can find an endless supply of laugh-out-loud jokes, lovable characters, life hacks, music, magic, gaming and more!

title: Christopher Cross: The Best Of [Greatest Hits Playlist: This Is Christopher Cross]
description:
This is The Best of Christopher Cross (cristopercross). A greatest hits playlist featuring Cross' iconic hits "Sailing", "Arthur's Theme (Best That You Can Do) [New York City Song]", "Ride Like The Wind", "Think Of Laura", "I Will (Take You Forever)", "All Right (Pingüino Rodríguez)" and many more.

Sign up to Christopher Cross HQ's Mailing List: https://seeker.fm/ccmailinglist

BEST OF CHRISTOPHER CROSS TRACKLIST
00:00 Sailing
04:17 Arthur's Theme (Best That You Can Do) [New York City Song] / Tema de Arturo
08:09 Ride Like The Wind / Run Like The Wind
12:40 Never Be The Same
17:23 All Right (Pingüino Rodríguez)
21:41 Think Of Laura
25:06 With Me Now
29:43 I Will (Take You Forever)
33:39 Talking In My Sleep
37:16 Swept Away
41:38 Open Up My Window
45:49 Is There Something
50:43 In The Blink Of An Eye
55:05 Say You'll Be Mine
58:01 The Light Is On

Christopher Cross burst onto the music scene with his 1979 self-titled debut album produced by Michael Omartian. The lead single “Ride Like The Wind” spent 4 weeks at #2 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart, and was quickly followed up by Cross’ most popular single to date (and first #1 hit) “Sailing”, which later became known as the archetype for the Yacht Rock genre. In 1981, Cross became the first artist in Grammy history to win the “Big Four” most prestigious awards in a single night; Record of the Year (for the single “Sailing”), Album of the Year, Song of the Year (also “Sailing”), and Best New Artist. Later that year Cross released “Arthur’s Theme (Best That You Can Do)” which he co-wrote with Burt Bacharach, Carole Bayer, Peter Allen, and was the title-theme for the 1981 film “Arthur” starring Dudley Moorre and Liza Minnelli. The song earned Cross his second #1 and the Oscar for Best Original Song at the 1981 Academy Awards. Cross’ sophomore album “Another Page” was released in 1983 and featured the singles “Think of Laura” and “All Right”.

title: Redferrin - Just Like Johnny (Official Music Video)
description:
Redferrin - Just Like Johnny (Official Music Video)

🔔  Subscribe🔔

Stay Connected With Redferrin: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/redferrin
Twitter: https://twitter.com/redferrin
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/redferrin/
TikTok: http://tiktok.com/@redferrin

In many ways, Warner Music Nashville’s rising artist Redferrin is a musical version of the famous Jack Daniels Old No. 7 blend. Made in Tennessee just like the whiskey, the singer-songwriter is emerging from behind the scenes of country’s edgy new post-modern era. He packs a punch you can’t ignore, and although his mix of country heart and hip-hop swagger might be an acquired taste, he’s been bringing fans a full-bodied buzz for years now – most recently with his viral hit “Jack & Diet Coke,” which has surpassed 25 million global streams and charted on Spotify’s Viral 50 (US) chart. But with his long-awaited Old No. 7 debut, out February 16, those fans can now savor their buzz longer than ever. Each song on the EP was co-produced by Redferrin himself – another important new ingredient making Old No. 7 his most potent (and exciting) small-batch yet. Best known as a collaborator, his co-written hits include good-timing anthems by early believers Florida Georgia Line – tracks like “Lil Bit” (featuring Nelly), “New Truck,” “Countryside” and more, plus a record-breaking Canadian No. 1, “Can’t Help Myself” by Dean Brody & The Reklaws. No longer sending his best songs away, Redferrin is all-in on his artistic vision. The man behind the scenes is now stepping into the spotlight and it’s about time. The 2024 Amazon Breakthrough Artist to Watch has amassed over 60 million global streams so far and will tour across the country throughout the year with artists such as Niko Moon and more. For more information, please visit https://www.redferrin.com/

© 2024 Warner Music Nashville LLC

Synopsis:
Kabhi Kabhie is the story of a poet Amit (Amitabh Bachchan) and the beautiful Pooja (Rakhee). It is the story of how these two visualize a perfect future together. But destiny has other plans, as Pooja bows to the wishes of her parents and marries Vijay (Shashi Kapoor). Amit drifts away from his poetry in a futile and unsuccessful attempt to forget Pooja he marries Anjali (Waheeda Rehman). But just how picture perfect are Amit and Pooja’s lives?

Some 20 years on... spanning over to the next generation, Pooja and Vijay’s son Vicky (Rishi Kapoor) and Anjali’s daughter Pinky (Neetu Singh) from a prior relationship, fall in love. A chain of events brings together old lovers as friends.

Kabhi Kabhie is a love story of generations.

description:
Im neuen Video zum lustigen Kinderlied kommt ein Elefant bei der Hurra Kinderlieder Familie zu Besuch – doch dort ist alles zu klein für ihn! Auch mit Auto, Bahn oder Fahrrad in die Ferien zu reisen ist für den Elefanten gar nicht so einfach. Aber im Badeparadies hat er großen Spaß. Ein witziger und spritziger Song für die ganze Familie!
 
Für mehr lustige Kinderlieder-Videos abonniere einfach unseren Hurra Kinderlieder Kanal: http://bit.ly/HurraKinderlieder 
... oder entdecke unsere "Hurra Kinderlieder" Musik als CD, Download oder zum Streamen und auf DVD: https://www.universal-music.de/hurra-kinderlieder
 
Hier der Liedtext von "Der Elefant“ zum Mitsingen:
 
Der Elefant kommt zu Besuch
Unser Haus ist viel zu klein
Für dieses große graue Tier
Müsste alles größer sein
 
Der Elefant passt nicht in die Wanne
Der Elefant passt nicht an den Tisch 
Der Elefant passt nicht auf die Toilette
Auch in ein Bettchen passt er nicht
 
Der Elefant hat Ferien
Da will er in den Sonnenschein
Womit soll er auf Reisen gehen?
Es ist alles viel zu klein
 
Der Elefant passt nicht in ein Auto
Der Elefant passt nicht in die Bahn
Der Elefant passt nicht in ein Flugzeug
Und kann auch nicht Fahrradfahren
 
„Flatter mit deinen Ohren, dann kannst du segeln! Hui!“
 
Der Elefant will baden gehen
Ja das macht ihm Riesenspaß
Er tapst ins Badeparadies
Und spritzt da alles nass
 
Der Elefant duscht den Bademeister
Der Elefant springt vom Drei-Meter-Brett
Der Elefant rutscht sogar auf der Rutsche
Und saugt das warme Wasser weg
 
„He Moment mal! Das schöne warme Wasser …“
 
Ein Lied von "Hurra Kinderlieder"

Holy Forever / Agnus Dei - Awaken Generation Music (feat. Alarice)
description:
'Holy Forever' & 'Agnus Dei' presented by Awaken Generation Music. Recorded live in Singapore. 

Holy Forever: Original Music by Jenn Johnson, Brian Johnson, Chris Tomlin, Jason Ingram, and Phil Wickham
Agnus Dei: Original Music by Michael W. Smith
_______
Awaken Generation Music is a thriving collective of songwriters and musicians based in Singapore. Originally birthed from a worship music school, the band brings together both professional and novice songwriters to create a fresh sound for the nations.  

Since the release of its debut EP Sons & Daughters Live Recording (2015) to its latest single, Worth It All (2023) recorded at Bethesda Cathedral, Awaken Generation Music’s mission is simple but clear: to see lives transformed by Christ through worship music and prophetic expression.
_____
WE HAVE A WORSHIP SCHOOL! Join our one year part time worship mentorship school. You will be mentored in your heart and skill as a singer, musician and leader. More details here: https://www.awakengeneration.sg/school

We also have an online school for those outside of Singapore. https://www.awakengeneration.sg/school

description:
Urejesho ni mchakato wa kurudisha kitu kilichoharibika au kupotea. Biblia inatuhimiza kumgeukia Mungu. Na kupitia imani na maombi, tutapata uponyaji, kurejeshewa nguvu, na kupewa maisha mapya katika Kristo Yesu.

‭Yer‬emia 30:17‬ 
Maana nitakurudishia afya, nami nitakuponya jeraha zako, asema BWANA ...
‭‭Yoe‬li ‭2:25‬ ‭
Nami nitawarudishia hiyo miaka iliyoliwa na nzige, na parare, na madumadu, na tunutu, jeshi langu kubwa nililotuma kati yenu.

Mnamo mwaka 2022, Familia ya Ev. Mchome, ilipitia kipindi kigumu sana baada ya kumpoteza mama yao mpendwa (Aliyeanguka ghafla na kufariki). Majonzi na simanzi kubwa ilitanda mioyoni mwao mithili ya wingu zito na giza totoro, hakuna maneno mazuri ambayo yangetosha kuwapa faraja familia hii.

Na hapa ndipo yalipatikana Mafunuo ya wimbo huu: Full story link - https://youtu.be/P8koCqEcu-M?si=wS-vsSVNPQo09zxV

Synopsis:
DIL TO PAGAL HAI is the story of Rahul (Shah Rukh Khan), who does not believe in love. Rahul fails to understand how two people can spend their lives together.

It is the story of Pooja (Madhuri Dixit), who believes that there is someone who is made for her and she is destined to meet that person.

It is also the story of Nisha (Karisma Kapoor) who believes that love is friendship and one day her dream will come true.

Dil To Pagal Hai is a grand musical about passionate people with dreams. Will their dreams come true? Will they find their true love?

Dil To Pagal Hai makes us believe that - someone... somewhere... is made for us.

*Empfohlen ab 12 Jahren*
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 

Bei "The Voice Kids" dürfen die jüngsten  Talente zeigen, was in ihnen steckt! Dabei zählt nur die Stimme: Denn während ihres Auftritts in den Blind Auditions sind die Coach-Sessel in Richtung des Publikums ausgerichtet, sodass die Coaches nicht sehen, wer auf der Bühne steht.
Wenn sie ein Talent in ihr Team holen möchten, drücken sie auf den Buzzer und der Sänger oder die Sängerin ist eine Runde weiter. Falls mehrere Coaches buzzern, hat das Talent freie Wahl. 
Nach den Blind Auditions folgen die Battles, in denen die Talente gegeneinander antreten, um in die Sing-Offs zu kommen! 
Nur wer sich hier abermals durchsetzt, schafft es in die alles ersehnten Finals - und hier entscheidet sich letztendlich, welches Talent welchen Teams mit einer atemberaubenden Stimme überzeugen kann und "The Voice Kids" gewinnt!

tags: Amethyst Music, Lyrics, Music, Lukas Graham, 7 Years
title: Lukas Graham - 7 Years (Lyrics)
description:
🔔 Turn on notifications to stay updated with new uploads!
🎤 Lyrics:

[Chorus 1]
Once I was seven years old my momma told me
Go make yourself some friends or you'll be lonely
Once I was seven years old

[Verse 1]
It was a big big world, but we thought we were bigger
Pushing each other to the limits, we were learning quicker
By eleven smoking herb and drinking burning liquor
Never rich so we were out to make that steady figure

[Chorus 2]
Once I was 11 years old my daddy told me
Go get yourself a wife or you'll be lonely
Once I was 11 years old

[Verse 2]
I always had that dream like my daddy before me
So I started writing songs, I started writing stories
Something about that glory just always seemed to bore me
Cause only those I really love will ever really know me

[Chorus 3]
Once I was 20 years old, my story got told
Before the morning sun, when life was lonely
Once I was 20 years old

(Lukas Graham!!!)

[Verse 3]
I only see my goals, I don't believe in failure
Cause I know the smallest voices, they can make it major
I got my boys with me at least those in favor
And if we don't meet before I leave, I hope I'll see you later

[Chorus 4]
Once I was 20 years old, my story got told
I was writing 'bout everything, I saw before me
Once I was 20 years old
Soon we'll be 30 years old, our songs have been sold
We've traveled around the world and we're still roaming
Soon we'll be 30 years old

[Verse 4]
I'm still learning about life
My woman brought children for me
So I can sing them all my songs
And I can tell them stories
Most of my boys are with me
Some are still out seeking glory
And some I had to leave behind
My brother I'm still sorry

[Bridge]
Soon I'll be 60 years old, my daddy got 61
Remember life and then your life becomes a better one
I made a man so happy when I wrote a letter once
I hope my children come and visit, once or twice a month

[Chorus 5]
Soon I'll be 60 years old, will I think the world is cold
Or will I have a lot of children who can warm me
Soon I'll be 60 years old
Soon I'll be 60 years old, will I think the world is cold
Or will I have a lot of children who can hold me
Soon I'll be 60 years old

[Outro]
Once I was seven years old, my momma told me
Go make yourself some friends or you'll be lonely
Once I was seven years old

Once I was seven years old

A peaceful classical music playlist for stress relief, relaxation, and meditation featuring some of the most beautiful pieces of classical music. Perfect to enjoy at the end of a long day, or during stressful times to relieve any anxiety. These soothing, tranquil classical melodies will help you unwind and quiet the noise of everyday life. Classical music can be a powerful tool for relieving the stress of everyday life - helping you relax and sleep better. It’s almost impossible to hear these pieces and not feel relaxed and happier afterwards!

title: Music for Work — Deep Focus Mix for Programming, Coding
description:
This carefully curated mix of tracks is designed specifically to help you focus on programming and coding. Dark and cyber electronic music in genres like chillstep and future garage will create the perfect background for working on complex projects or completing routine tasks. Thanks to the futuristic atmosphere of this musical accompaniment, you will be able to immerse yourself in the creative process with special depth and inspiration. These tracks will help you maintain a high level of concentration and productivity to achieve maximum results. Discover new horizons of efficiency with our specially curated musical accompaniment

🎯Tips for Deep Focus and Concentration:
1. Movement Meditation: Try practicing movement meditation, such as yoga, tai chi, or walking in a natural environment. This will help clear your mind, improve focus, and reduce stress levels.
2. Polyphasic Sleep: Explore polyphasic sleep methods, which involve taking short periods of sleep throughout the day to enhance your concentration and productivity. Some people find that it allows them to reduce overall sleep time and remain more alert during the day.
3. Color Therapy: Use colors to manage your mood and energy levels. For example, different shades of blue and green can promote calmness and focus, while bright colors like orange or red can stimulate activity and energy.
4. Nature Contemplation Practice: Spend time outdoors, immersing yourself in the natural beauty and sounds of the environment. This can help calm your mind, reduce stress, and increase concentration.
5. Music therapy with our Chill Music Lab playlists: Listen to our playlists or radio, which include relaxing and focusing tracks. Such music can help improve concentration and create a calm working atmosphere for your goals.

title: Jenna Davis - 6FT Nothing (Official Music Video)
description:
Jenna Davis - 6FT Nothing (Official Music Video) HEY guys it's Jenna Davis! Sit back and enjoy watching the official music video for my newest single "6FT Nothing". I wrote the first lyric of this song "6'2 was pretty cute but he had an attitude" and stored it in the notes of my phone for weeks. One morning, I sat down at Liz Rose Music in Nashville TN, and pulled up the lyric. I expressed I have always wanted to write a song based on the guys I have had flings with and what had happened (AKA why we didn't work out 👀) & just like that....I wrote 6FT Nothing with two of my favorite people. I am so incredibly proud of this song & music video! This is the first single off my upcoming project so more music coming soon 😏

▸  Another snapshot of a brilliant #broadwaymusicals moment.
▸  Step back in time with this unforgettable performance of "You'll Be Back" by 2024 Tony Award Winner Jonathan Groff (Congratulations Jonathan!!), portraying King George III in the smash-hit Broadway musical, Hamilton! 
▸  Written by Lin-Manuel Miranda, Hamilton blends hip-hop, jazz, R&B, and Broadway to tell the story of American Founding Father Alexander Hamilton
▸  In this iconic number, King George III delivers a hilariously passive-aggressive message to the American colonists, warning them of the consequences of their rebellion. 
▸  Jonathan Groff captivates the audience with his brilliant portrayal of the charming yet menacing monarch.
▸  His impeccable timing, sharp wit, and vocal prowess make this performance a standout moment in the musical.
▸  The catchy tune, witty lyrics, and Groff's impeccable delivery will have you singing along and laughing out loud.
🔻

Presenting the lyric video of the timeless love song ‘Dekhha Tenu’ from the film ‘Mr. and Mrs. Mahi’ - out now! The song speaks of passion and how losing everything means nothing and losing one’s beloved means that everything is lost.

description:
🎵 Dive into a journey of nostalgia and heartache with "Jaane Kyun" by Tanveer Evan. In this soul-stirring composition, Tanveer Evan beautifully captures the essence of cherishing old memories while grappling with heartbreak.With poignant lyrics and haunting melodies, Tanveer Evan pours his heart out in every note.
Experience the raw emotions of heartbreak through "Jaane Kyun", a soulful composition by Tanveer Evan.
Let the music resonate with your own journey of love and loss as you immerse yourself in this heartfelt creation.Feel the depths of "Jaane Kyun".

Hum mile kahi

Release Date: 27 February 1976

Watch all videos from the film ‘Kabhi Kabhie’: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE5AAC17E7AAB025B

Synopsis:
Kabhi Kabhie is the story of a poet Amit (Amitabh Bachchan) and the beautiful Pooja (Rakhee). It is the story of how these two visualize a perfect future together. But destiny has other plans, as Pooja bows to the wishes of her parents and marries Vijay (Shashi Kapoor). Amit drifts away from his poetry in a futile and unsuccessful attempt to forget Pooja he marries Anjali (Waheeda Rehman). But just how picture perfect are Amit and Pooja’s lives?

Some 20 years on... spanning over to the next generation, Pooja and Vijay’s son Vicky (Rishi Kapoor) and Anjali’s daughter Pinky (Neetu Singh) from a prior relationship, fall in love. A chain of events brings together old lovers as friends.

Kabhi Kabhie is a love story of generations.

description:
New episodes streaming Fridays with the Paramount+ with SHOWTIME plan.

Paramount+ is the streaming home of SHOWTIME. Stream The Chi with the Paramount+ with SHOWTIME plan. Try it free today: https://prmntpl.us/PPlusYT  

Subscribe to The Chi channel: https://goo.gl/ErZxti  

Check out our official Spotify playlist to stream music from The Chi: https://spoti.fi/3p3zhUj 

About Season 6 of The Chi: This season, life in THE CHI reverberates between the highest highs and lowest lows. Big dreams are finally realized but at a cost and everyone will be tested in unimaginable ways as they calculate the risks and rewards of their next big move. Emmett (Jacob Latimore) and Kiesha’s (Birgundi Baker) blissful blended union is tested by his insatiable drive to expand Smokey’s and a new perilous partnership, while Kiesha finally races toward a rewarding new career. Douda (Curtiss Cook) deals with the fallout of Q’s murder and its effect on the shifting loyalty of his inner circle. Victor’s (Luke James) bold declaration of love for both his new girlfriend and his beloved community will impact his political ambitions. Happily married Jada (Yolonda Ross) mentors Emmett and her besties as they navigate relationships. Kevin (Alex Hibbert) is becoming a brilliant master gamer but struggles with the youthful pitfalls of early independence. Jake (Michael V. Epps) launches a new business, and Papa (Shamon Brown Jr.) falls for an older woman while questioning his faith. What will become of their pursuits will be revealed over the course of this season’s sixteen jaw-dropping episodes.  

About The Chi on SHOWTIME: On Chicago's south side, an average day finds kids prepping for school as their parents head off to work, young adults trying to make a living, and the elders keeping an eye on things from their front porches. But in this tough neighborhood, real dangers threaten daily to squelch dreams, and the simplest decisions can have life or death consequences. From Emmy® winner Lena Waithe, The Chi is a timely coming-of-age drama series centered on a group of residents who become linked by coincidence but bonded by the need for connection and redemption.

title: Ruger, Bnxn - Bae Bae (Live Session) | Vevo ctrl
description:
Ruger & Bnxn - Bae Bae - Live Session | Vevo ctrl 

It’s hard to believe Ruger and Bnxn were recently, as they discussed with Billboard, in a “beef.” Both chill Nigerian dudes, they’re natural partners, quick to laugh and well-skilled at fashioning catchy tunes. We saw that synchrony firsthand when they hopped into our London studio during the promo grind for their surprise collab album, ‘RnB.’ While its title is a sly play on words that, in part, points to American groove music, R and B linking up is a significant moment for their home continent’s main musical export. “For Afrobeats right now, many of us don’t work together, many of us don’t drop joint projects like that,” the wily Ruger has explained. If ‘RnB’ was promoted to their respective stan armies as a call for online unification, then “Ilashé” has been the ultimate peacemaker. It’s an undeniably catchy tune, and sounds even better when you watch the duo bounce around our ctrl stage. For a sugary chaser, pink house lights matched the rose-colored romanticism of “Bae Bae.” Afterwards, we grabbed them for a Footnotes interview about the airline shenanigans of their “POE” video. “To our surprise the TSA security guys were cool,” laughed Bnxn. Clearly, no one can deny their collective good energy.

title: My new single Burn is out now. #NewMusic #Burn #BoyGolden #Music
description:
My new single Burn is out now. I feel that songs often come true, whether I want them to or not. I remember writing this song before I we really started playing live, but I knew what I wanted - I wanted a band full of my friends I could share with the world. I wanted the music to be hot, shit hot, every night. This song is a dream, a dream I have almost realized - I do in fact get to play great music with my friends all the time. Couldn’t be any luckier!

Pre-sale for my tour this fall also started today. Join my Laylo for the password.

My first and only Black Screen Pure Nature Rain and Incredible Present Thunder Sounds 24/7 Livestream. The only one, because I turned a decent recording into this composition and I think that you don't need any other videos for it. title: Till the Clouds Roll By 1949 (Musical, Biography) Lena Horne, Frank Sinatra, Judy Garland
description:
The mammoth musical of Jerome Kern's dramatic life story! 
Biography of songwriter, Broadway pioneer, Jerome Kern. Unable to find immediate success in the USA, Kern sought recognition abroad. He journeyed to England where his dreams of success became real and where he met his future wife Eva.

Original title: Till the Clouds Roll By (1949) AKA: Silver Lining

This film is available with original english audio, and dubbed French, Portuguese & Spanish.  And subtitled in many more language options. 

Directors: Richard Whorf, Vincente Minnelli
Writers: Guy Bolton, George Wells
Stars: Robert Walker, Van Heflin, Lucille Bremer, Lena Horne, Frank Sinatra, Judy Garland, Angela Lansbury
Genres: Classics, Biography, Musical
Budget: $2,841,000 (estimated)

title: How to REMIX a Remix 🎬✨
description:
You can now Remix a Remix to add on to other Shorts! Here’s how.

When viewing a Short that was created with any of our Remix features, tap the Remix icon and select Use this Sound, Collab, Green Screen, or Cut to use a part of that Short in your own Short.

Once you select one of these options, trim to select the part of the Short you want to Remix. Then, start recording to add onto the Short.

Adding onto a Remixed Short is a fun way to add to previous Remixes. Whether it’s performing in a musical chain or creating a physical illusion, Remixing lets you easily join in on the fun and express yourself.

What will you create with Remix? Subscribe to the YouTube Creators channel for more tips and updates!

title: Jehova es mi pastor (Salmos 23)
description:
Si no te quieres perder de ninguno de mis vídeos te invito a que te suscribas al canal y actives la campanita de notificaciones🔔

Jehová es mi pastor; nada me faltará.

En lugares de delicados pastos me hará descansar;
Junto a aguas de reposo me pastoreará.

Confortará mi alma;
Me guiará por sendas de justicia por amor de su nombre.

Aunque ande en valle de sombra de muerte,
No temeré mal alguno, porque tú estarás conmigo;
Tu vara y tu cayado me infundirán aliento.

Aderezas mesa delante de mí en presencia de mis angustiadores;
Unges mi cabeza con aceite; mi copa está rebosando.

Ciertamente el bien y la misericordia me seguirán todos los días de mi vida,
Y en la casa de Jehová moraré por largos días.

description:

★ Follow TCDB on https://ko-fi.com/tcdbinfo to get notified of every new post — it's free and easy!

☑ About This Video 
My previous upload of The Cure's MTV Unplugged is now blocked on YouTube in all territories but you can still watch it by following the link above.

All 9 currently available songs from The Cure's acoustic live performance for "MTV Unplugged". The shooting of this show took 3 hours, with 12 songs performed (including "In Your House", "M" and "Time Has Told Me", a Nick Drake cover) and at least 3 repetitions.

Tracklist:
1 -- Let's Go to Bed [00:00]
2 -- Just Like Heaven [03:57]
3 -- The Caterpillar [7:44]
4 -- The Blood [11:35]
5 -- Boys Don't Cry [15:25]
6 -- The Walk [18:37]
7 -- A Letter to Elise [22:06]
8 -- If Only Tonight We Could Sleep [26:55]
9 -- Lullaby [30:35]

Edited using the following 4 sources: 
[1] Tracks 1-6
A HD (720p) version of "MTV Unplugged" that aired on MTV Russia on 2018-10-14. Parts with Russian overdub have been replaced with the original audio from Source 4.
Taken from / Thanks to: unknown

[2] Tracks 7-8
A Full HD (1080p) version of The Cure's "Play Out" that looks like an upscale from an SD version. At least the picture of Source 1 has more details. 
Taken from / Thanks to: @thecure 

[3] Track 9
A Full HD (1080p) version of the performance that aired on MTV Hits' 'MTV Classic Hitlist' program sometime during the 2000s and appears to be an upscale from an SD version.
Taken from / Thanks to: @matiasadrianozarategarciacalde 

[4] Tracks 1-6
Audio recording of the original "MTV Unplugged" program.
Taken from / Thanks to: unknown

Are you a Marvel fan looking to catch up on all the movies before the new releases? Here's a guide to watching the Marvel Cinematic Universe in order.

Start with Phase One, beginning with Iron Man and follow the journey of Tony Stark as he becomes Iron Man. Then watch The Incredible Hulk, Thor, and Captain America: The First Avenger to complete Phase One.

Move on to Phase Two with Iron Man 3, Thor: The Dark World, Captain America: The Winter Soldier, Guardians of the Galaxy, Avengers: Age of Ultron, and Ant-Man.

Next up is Phase Three, which includes Captain America: Civil War, Doctor Strange, Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2, Spider-Man: Homecoming, Thor: Ragnarok, Black Panther, Avengers: Infinity War, Ant-Man and The Wasp, Captain Marvel, and Avengers: Endgame.

Finally, watch Spider-Man: Far From Home and Black Widow to complete your Marvel movie marathon.

By watching all these movies in order, you'll have a better understanding of the characters and storylines leading up to the new releases.

title: Adventures of the Wilderness Family 2
description: This heartpounding sequel to The Adventures Of The Wilderness Family continues the saga of the family who chose to live in their peaceful log cabin home in the Rockies over fast-paced big city life. They now face terrifying times in fierce winter storms, an avalanche, and being attacked by a ferocious pack of hungry wolves. Watch as America's favorite family stands strong together to prove that the best things in life are really free. Share in the adventures of a lifetime as this internationally loved cast returns for the second chapter of the Wilderness Family trilogy. The Adventures Of The Wilderness Family, Wilderness Family Part II, and Mountain Family Robinson.

title: LEAPFROG: THE AMAZING ALPHABET AMUSEMENT PARK
description: Help Lily, Tad, and Scout find the letters to start the fun at the amusement park! When their firefly friend, Edison, takes Tad, Lily and Scout to the place of his childhood dreams, the gang is shocked to discover that Alistair Alphabelly's Amazing Amusement Park is... closed! To make matters worse, Edison has gotten himself stuck atop the Amazing Alphabet Ferris Wheel. The only way to save him is to turn on the rides in the park with the magic of the alphabet. Now the children must learn all of the letters, big and small, to save their friend, save the day and perhaps even meet the rhyme master himself, Alistair Alphabelly!

title: Healing Frequency Meditation (1111 Hz) | 1 hour handpan music | Malte Marten & Lynxk
description:
I am so proud and happy to share this jam with you. Lynxk and I met a couple of weeks ago, when she had just started her handpan journey. In the meantime we did some handpan lessons and started playing gentle jams together. Her talent and openness is amazing and from a teachers perspective it just makes my heart smile to see her progress. We’ve been focusing on the very basics of handpan playing - the foundation of every jam: the chord progression. Goal of the first learning cycle is to deepen the understanding of the continuous change of chords. Next on is to implement new patterns, first percussive elements and little fill-ins to make one and the same pattern sound unique.
On a personal note it is deeply fulfilling to jam with her. The energy shifts as soon as we take the instruments on our labs and start to play. Sending love always ♾️🤍

See me live:
https://maltemarten.com/shows

Listen to my full album "Healing Frequencies" now:
https://open.spotify.com/intl-de/album/71a6eE54atrYTJVVu6Ay5b

If you also want to start learning with me, join my free mini class and start today!
https://www.maltemartenmethod.com/free-mini-class

Join my mailinglist to unlock my secret album and access my exclusive handpan learning videos for free:
https://www.maltemarten.com

Lynxk played on a F# Low Pygmy and Malte on a D Aegean Handpan made by @AyasaInstruments

Recorded on a golden meadow in the Black Forest.

The official YouTube channel of Cody Johnson.
 
Cody Johnson has established a following of passionately loyal fans who regularly sell out shows across the country. The artist that media has touted “just might be the future of real country music” has skyrocketed success with numerous celebrated albums: Leather Deluxe Edition, Leather, Human The Double Album, A Cody Johnson Christmas, Cody Johnson & The Rockin’ CJB Live, and Ain’t Nothin’ To It plus an award-winning feature-length documentary “Dear Rodeo: The Cody Johnson Story.” Cody has 42 Gold and Platinum certifications, has nearly 8 billion global streams and three #1 singles. 

Cody’s brand-new studio project Leather Deluxe Edition is out now. The deluxe album contains 13 brand new tracks and also includes all 12 songs from his Leather album released last November for a total of 25 songs. Produced by Trent Willmon, the album is available in stores, including vinyl, and at all digital retailers and streaming platforms HERE.

Cody has five nominations for the upcoming “The 58th Annual CMA Awards” including Male Vocalist of the Year, Album of the Year for Leather, Single of the Year for “Dirt Cheap” and two nominations in Music Video of the Year for both “The Painter” and “Dirt Cheap.” The CMA Awards will be broadcast live from Nashville’s Bridgestone Arena Wednesday, November 20 on ABC and the next day on Hulu.

His numerous industry honors include recognition as a CMT Artist of The Year, three CMT Music Awards wins, two CMA Awards, being named “Best New Country Artist” at the iHeart Music. His #1 His television appearances have entertained fans on the Today Show, the Kelly Clarkson Show and the Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon in addition to outstanding live tv performances at the iHeart Music Awards, the ACM Awards, CMA Awards, CMT Music Awards, CMT Giants honoring Vince Gill, and the CMT Artist of the Year Special.

title: ADLEY PLAYS a MAGiCAL PiANO!! adley pretends to play a new song that sounds a little familiar 🤔 🎹📱
description:
HEY EVERYBODY!! Today’s video is full of magic because ADLEY PLAYS a MAGiCAL PiANO!! 🎹✨ I was pretending to play a brand-new song, but it started to sound a little familiar... 🤔📱

I found this super cool piano at CrunchLabs that plays music all by itself! I tried to make up my own song, but every time I pressed a key, it played a tune I knew! It was like the piano could read my mind or had a magical memory of its own! 🎶🌟

I couldn’t stop giggling as I pretended to be a piano pro, and the magical piano kept surprising me with familiar tunes. It was so much fun playing along and trying to guess what song would come next! 😄🎵

Make sure to watch the whole video to see all the magical music moments and the fun we had with the piano! 💖✨

See you in the next video! Byeee! 🥳👋

title: LYCINAÏS JEAN - DANJE (FEAT. RDYDY & JAZZYKEY) OFFICIAL VIDEO
description:
#konpa #haiti #haitianmusic #lycinaïsjean 
Hello la famille, j'espère que ce titre vous procurera autant de plaisir qu'on en a eu avec les deux beatmakers Rdydy et Jazzy Key lorsqu'on le préparait ensemble ! Il me tenait à coeur depuis longtemps de faire un vrai clin d'oeil à la communauté haïtienne qui me suit, car j'ai un grand respect pour cette Nation qu'est Haïti... elle représente beaucoup dans le paysage Antillais historiquement parlant, et j'en suis fière comme si j'en étais originaire !
Et puis... ce n'est plus un secret pour vous: je suis une antillaise qui ADORE le KONPA !
Sauf que cette fois il était important pour moi de reprendre les codes musicaux y compris le créole Haïtien du début à la fin du morceau. Le créole est pour moi l'une des langues les plus adaptées pour parler d'amour et de choses profondes. 
Vous ne trouvez pas ? Je vous laisse apprécier...

Het officiële YouTube kanaal van POPZ. POPZ is de nieuwste kinderpopgroep van Nederland. POPZ verbindt kinderen door de beste en populairste muziek. Alle nummers worden gezongen “door kinderen voor kinderen”. POPZ bestaat uit getalenteerde zang- en danstalenten in de leeftijd van 8 tot en met 13 jaar. POPZ bestaat uit: Pien, Jason, Lizzy, Xiao Song, Sanne, Sophie, Jurre, Stan, Zoë Billy, Linde, Lotte, Fien, Emma en Fay. De allereerste single “Iedereen naar buiten” is hèt buitenspeellied van 2023. Een samenwerking met Jantje Beton en Nickelodeon voor de Nationale Buitenspeeldag. Abonneer je op het kanaal van POPZ voor videoclips, official audio video’s, lyric video’s, dansinstructies, exclusieve POPZ interviews, POPZ-vlogs en beelden van achter de schermen.

title: Weezer - Buddy Holly (2024 Remaster)
description:
Blue 30 CD & Vinyl box sets available now https://weezerwebstore.com

You get a full disc of unreleased early recordings, a full disc of unreleased early live recordings, The Kitchen Tape in its fully realized album format (as the band hoped would be possible back in '92, but never happened till now), The early 1995 BBC sessions in their entirely, and a 7" of the entire 1993 LMU Sessions which was the source of "Jamie”!

Box sets also include a 24 page full color Weezine by Karl with exclusive photos, extensive history, & credits, 4 lithographs feat. dozens of never before seen band photos from the Blue Album photo shoot, a special sticker sheet representing the 10 Blue songs, a 12 sided die for all your Dungeon Mastering needs, & a stylish pin of our mascot Bokkus, first seen inside the booklet of the Blue Album. All packaged in a really cool "unraveling" sweater box!

Order now: https://weezerwebstore.com

title: 60 Lagu Nostalgia 90an 2000an  - Terpopuler Tembang Kenangan Abadi 2024 || Dewa19,Ari Lasso, TIPE X
description:
Setelah tahun 2000-an muncul konsep-konsep baru seperti musik kontemporer, musik pasar, folk kontemporer... Saat ini, musik anak muda (musik ringan) sudah menjadi konsep besar yang merujuk pada musik populer dan merupakan salah satu dari tiga segmen besar musik vokal Indonesia saat ini (lagu cinta, musik daerah, musik ringan). Musik lebih menyatu dengan dunia, selain Pop Ballad dan Rock yang populer, ada juga Jazz/Blues,... Terkadang (di kalangan masyarakat, bukan profesional) musik remaja digunakan untuk membedakan dengan musik ringan dengan musik yang lebih sedikit melodi seru (disebut juga musik biru) muncul pada dekade-dekade sebelumnya Dengan partisipasi musisi, penyanyi dan band ternama seperti Ari Lasso, TIPE-X, Melly Goeslaw, Dewa 19, Agnes Monica... dengan Lagu-Lagu yang Membawa Banyak Makna di Dalamnya. Kehidupan....
INGAT UNTUK MENDAFTAR DAN IKUTI SALURAN INI UNTUK MENDAPATKAN MENIT YANG NYAMAN MENDENGARKAN MUSIK SAAT BEKERJA

Deep Focus Radio — Music for Coding & Productivity
description:
This livestream with a carefully curated mix of tracks is designed specifically to help you focus on programming and coding. Dark and cyber electronic music radio in genres like chillstep and future garage will create the perfect background for working on complex projects or completing routine tasks. Thanks to the futuristic atmosphere of this musical accompaniment, you will be able to immerse yourself in the creative process with special depth and inspiration. These tracks will help you maintain a high level of concentration and productivity to achieve maximum results. Discover new horizons of efficiency with our specially curated musical accompaniment. 

🎯Tips for Deep Focus and Concentration:
1. Movement Meditation: Try practicing movement meditation, such as yoga, tai chi, or walking in a natural environment. This will help clear your mind, improve focus, and reduce stress levels.
2. Polyphasic Sleep: Explore polyphasic sleep methods, which involve taking short periods of sleep throughout the day to enhance your concentration and productivity. Some people find that it allows them to reduce overall sleep time and remain more alert during the day.
3. Color Therapy: Use colors to manage your mood and energy levels. For example, different shades of blue and green can promote calmness and focus, while bright colors like orange or red can stimulate activity and energy.
4. Nature Contemplation Practice: Spend time outdoors, immersing yourself in the natural beauty and sounds of the environment. This can help calm your mind, reduce stress, and increase concentration.
5. Music therapy with our Chill Music Lab playlists: Listen to our playlists or radio, which include relaxing and focusing tracks. Such music can help improve concentration and create a calm working atmosphere for your goals.

title: Baby White Noise for Sleep & Colic Relief | No Ads While Sleeping!
description:
Sometimes it can be hard for your little one to get sleep at night. That struggle is amplified by the fact that babies can't communicate their needs, often leaving parents attempting every solution to get them to settle. If you find yourself in a similar situation with your baby, we may have the perfect solution for you! Baby white noise can be a powerful tool every parent should have on their utility belt! The consistent sleep sound creates a calming atmosphere that can help ease your babies colic. Additionally, baby white noise can help cover up outside sounds that keep your baby up at night. Not to mention, this sleep white noise sounds just like what babies heard in the womb, bringing a sense of familiarity with all that comfort! Millions of parents rely on white noise to sleep when they put their precious one to sleep. Next time your child is struggling to feel relaxed, you should give it a try too! You may never have another bedtime without it! 

While playing white noise for babies, it’s important to keep tabs on the volume, because any white noise machine, smartphone, or computer can put out levels that are too loud for your child. It's recommended to play the sound at least a few feet from where your infant is sleeping and to keep the volume no louder than the sound of a soft shower.

Parents can download an app to turn their smartphone into a sound level meter. One good, free, option is the sound level meter app created by the U.S. National Institutes for Occupational Safety and Health (NIOSH) available on the app store as the NIOSH SLM app.

For more white noise for babies, please check out:
Colicky Baby Sleeps To This Magic Sound: https://youtu.be/oewj_XEM1js
Baby White Noise Sleep Sounds: https://youtu.be/dhaozFzF4bg
White Noise for Your Baby | 10 Hour Sleep Sounds: https://youtu.be/cDa_LPNkpMA

#BabyWhiteNoise #Colicky #BabySleep #SleepSounds #WhiteNoiseForBabies #RelaxingWhiteNoise #WhiteNoise #Sleep

DISCLAIMER: Do not drive or operate heavy machinery while listening to this sound. Remember that loud sounds can potentially damage your hearing. When playing one of our videos, if you cannot have a conversation over the sound without raising your voice, the sound may be too loud for your ears. Please do not place speakers right next to a baby’s ears. If you have difficulty hearing or hear ringing in your ears, please immediately discontinue listening to the white noise sounds and consult an audiologist or your physician. 

The sounds provided by this Youtube channel are for entertainment purposes only and are not a treatment for sleep disorders or tinnitus. If you have significant difficulty sleeping on a regular basis, experience fitful/restless sleep, or feel tired during the day, please consult your physician.

Wyrażam ogromną wdzięczność dla Szefa z Góry za idealną pogodę nad Bałtykiem w dniu zdjęć!!!!

Specjalne Podziękowanie dla Danusi i Zenka Martyniuków za przeurocze spotkanie na planie i w studio. Za ciepło i normalność. Za waszą dobroć i życzliwość którą poczuliśmy i mam nadzieję, że uchwyciliśmy w naszym klipie.

Dla mojej żony Kajry za spełnienie mojego marzenia, pomysł na teledysk i nieustającą wiarę w moje piosenki
Dla Huberta za przebyte kilometry z obciążeniem, serducho i ogień
Dla Roberta za wsparcie na każdym etapie pracy nad ta piosenką i idealną lokalizację nad Bałtykiem.
Dla naszego sztabu Beauty Dagi Mikuły i Kasi Rudnik dzięki którym nasze żony wyglądają zjawiskowo, Zenek też a o mnie porozmawiamy przy kolejnej produkcji bo chciałbym wyglądać nieco młodziej 
Dla Pawła i Piotra Pilipienko dzięki którym to był najprzyjemniejszy dzień zdjęciowy w naszej karierze i najpiękniejsze kolory w klipie.
Gratuluje WAM najpiękniejszego Bałtyku w historii polskich teledysków 
Dla Łukasz Sienickiego za dni spędzone w studio, pasję i dożywianie przez uroczą żonę Lenę
Dla AMERYKAŃSKIEGO LEKTORA: Łukasza Nowickiego za udział w zwiastunie, i szybkość tygrysa
Dla mojego całego zespołu a szczególnie dla Piotra Aleksandrowicza za pracowitość i ogromne wsparcie moich pomysłów.

he song you've written is a deeply emotional piece that captures the pain and longing of unfulfilled promises. The lyrics revolve around the theme of waiting for someone who promised to come but never does, leading to a profound sense of disappointment and heartache. The repetition of the lines "তুমি আসবে বলেছিলে, তুমি এলে না এখনো" emphasizes the lingering hope that eventually turns into despair.

Key Elements of the Song:
Emotion of Waiting: The recurring lines and the imagery of sitting alone by the window during a rainy evening encapsulate the loneliness and the emotional turmoil of waiting.
Music and Ambiance: The mention of listening to Arijit's songs and counting the clock's ticking adds a layer of melancholic ambiance, enhancing the mood of the song.
Metaphors: The use of metaphors like "আমার মনের টুনটুনি বিরহে ছটফটায়" beautifully symbolizes the restless heart, aching in separation.
Tone: The tone of the song is somber and introspective, with a hint of frustration in the lines "তুমি কথা দিয়েও এলে না," expressing the betrayal of unkept promises.
Imagery: The song paints vivid pictures of a rainy evening, a solitary figure waiting, and a heart weighed down by unfulfilled expectations.
Overall, this song is a poignant reflection on the themes of love, loss, and the emotional toll of waiting for someone who may never return. It captures the essence of heartbreak in a poetic and relatable manner.

এই গানটি খুবই আবেগপ্রবণ, যেখানে অপূর্ণ প্রতিশ্রুতির বেদনা এবং অপেক্ষার যন্ত্রণা খুব সুন্দরভাবে ফুটিয়ে তোলা হয়েছে। গানের লিরিক্সে দেখা যায়, একজন অপেক্ষা করছে তার প্রিয়জনের জন্য, যে আসার প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়েছিল কিন্তু এখনো আসেনি। "তুমি আসবে বলেছিলে, তুমি এলে না এখনো" এই লাইনগুলোতে বারবার ফিরে আসা সেই অপেক্ষার আশা, যা ধীরে ধীরে হতাশায় রূপ নিচ্ছে।

গানের মূল বৈশিষ্ট্য:
অপেক্ষার অনুভূতি: "তুমি আসবে বলেছিলে" লাইনটি এবং বৃষ্টির সন্ধ্যায় জানালার পাশে একলা বসে থাকার চিত্রটি একাকীত্ব এবং অপেক্ষার যন্ত্রণাকে প্রকাশ করে।
সঙ্গীত ও পরিবেশ: আরিজিতের গানের উল্লেখ এবং ঘড়ির কাঁটা গুনতে থাকা গানের পরিবেশকে আরো বেশি আবেগময় এবং মলিন করে তোলে।
রূপক: "আমার মনের টুনটুনি বিরহে ছটফটায়" এই লাইনটি মনকে একটি ছোট পাখির সঙ্গে তুলনা করে, যে বিরহের কষ্টে ছটফট করছে।
টোন: গানের টোনটি নির্জন এবং অন্তর্মুখী, বিশেষ করে "তুমি কথা দিয়েও এলে না" এই লাইনটি প্রতিশ্রুতি রক্ষার ব্যর্থতার হতাশা প্রকাশ করে।
চিত্রকল্প: গানে বৃষ্টির সন্ধ্যা, একলা বসে থাকা, এবং প্রতিশ্রুতি না রাখা সম্পর্কিত চিত্রকল্পগুলি খুব সুন্দরভাবে ফুটিয়ে তোলা হয়েছে।

यह गीत अत्यंत भावनात्मक है, जिसमें अधूरे वादों की पीड़ा और इंतजार की कसक को बखूबी दर्शाया गया है। गीत के बोलों में, एक व्यक्ति अपने प्रियजन का इंतजार कर रहा है, जिसने आने का वादा किया था लेकिन अभी तक नहीं आया। "तुमी आसबे बोलेछिले, तुमी एले ना ऐखनो" इन लाइनों में बार-बार लौटने वाली वह उम्मीद है, जो धीरे-धीरे निराशा में बदल रही है।

गाने के मुख्य तत्व:
इंतजार की भावना: "तुमी आसबे बोलेछिले" लाइन और बारिश की शाम में खिड़की के पास अकेले बैठने का चित्रण अकेलेपन और इंतजार की पीड़ा को व्यक्त करता है।
संगीत और माहौल: अरिजीत के गीतों का जिक्र और घड़ी की टिक-टिक सुनने से गाने के माहौल को और भी भावुक और उदास बना देता है।
रूपक: "आमार मोनेर टुंटुनी बिरोहे छटपटाए" इस लाइन में मन की तुलना एक छोटे पक्षी से की गई है, जो विरह की पीड़ा में तड़प रहा है।
स्वर: गाने का स्वर उदासीन और अंतर्मुखी है, विशेष रूप से "तुमी कथा दिएओ एले ना" इस लाइन में वादे को निभाने में असफलता की निराशा झलकती है।
चित्रण: गाने में बारिश की शाम, अकेले बैठना, और वादे पूरे न करने से संबंधित चित्रण को खूबसूरती से उकेरा गया है।
इस गाने में प्यार, खोने और उस भावनात्मक तनाव की बात की गई है, जो किसी के लौटने का इंतजार करने में महसूस होती है। यह गीत दिल टूटने की भावना को बेहद खूबसूरत और संवेदनशील तरीके से पेश करता है।

title: MUSICAL TRAPPER #rapper #rapmusic #rapsong #treandingvideo
description:
The song is a self-affirming rap anthem that highlights the artist's journey and identity as a "musical trapper" and "peacekeeper." It combines introspective lyrics with a confident, assertive tone, emphasizing themes of authenticity, self-respect, and determination. The artist positions themselves as a truth-teller and trendsetter who values depth of thought ("think deeper, feel always upper") while staying true to their principles in a world full of challenges and deception.

Throughout the song, there's a focus on the artist's resilience and their commitment to chasing dreams and writing from the heart, rather than conforming to superficial standards. The recurring hook reinforces the core message of striving for something greater while maintaining a sense of integrity and peace. The song is both a declaration of the artist's individuality and a motivational piece encouraging listeners to pursue their own goals with a deep sense of purpose.
- Arpan

यह गीत इच्छाओं और ख्वाहिशों के विभिन्न पहलुओं पर आधारित है। इसमें दिल की प्यास, मोहब्बत की चाहत, जीत का जुनून, और ताकत की लालसा को खूबसूरती से बयां किया गया है। ख्वाहिशें कभी खुशी देती हैं, कभी दुख, और यही वे भावनाएँ हैं जो दुनिया को चलाती हैं।

And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road


I needed somewhere to take my mistakes
I didn’t want my family to see me cry
They’ll never know I’m 
carrying all of this weight 
Dealing with the pressure 
of trying to provide
No sign of struggle can show on my face
They ask if I’m OK I just flash them a smile
Fire up that engine to take me away
I’m speeding through emotions with every mile
On that road is where I find my peace
I remember daddy told me about some times like these
On that road is where my minds at ease
I keep driving life away, rejecting change so


When I need space that’s where I go
A place to escape that nobody knows 
Where I feel free to let things go
And face this evil that burdens my soul
I bring my hatred, I pack my pain
All the emotions I cannot explain
It’s where I found God
And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road


I tried my best to plant the seeds
And then I watered everything that was in my life
But as a man, the only flowers that you get
Are when you’re 6 feet under on the day you die
I think I feel the pain my father felt
It’s finally sinking in 
looking back all I see is his eyes
He said that house is not a home
Unless you build it on respect 
with some kids and a loving wife
If these walls could talk
I bet they’d say it’s all my fault
That I don’t try hard
That I ain’t man enough
That I ain’t standing up
That I just burn everything 
that my hands touch
If these walls could talk
I bet they’d say I’m to blame
That I’m the one who put myself inside of all of these chains
That my addictive personalities what ran them away
And that I hurt myself by staying quiet
And not explaining I’m broken
In places, I can’t even see
I know there’s gotta be a heaven
Because the hell that’s in me
Is taking a dangerous toll
That I’m paying with all of my soul


When I need space that’s where I go
A place to escape that nobody knows 
Where I feel free to let things go
And face this evil that burdens my soul
I bring my hatred I pack my pain
All the emotions I cannot explain
It’s where I found God
And filled that whole
It’s he, myself and I
On that lonely dirt road

__________________________________________________________________

If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. 2024 is going to bring our best and most impactful work. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. This is music for the PEOPLE, spread BY THE PEOPLE. Like, comment, share and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world.

title: Playlist songs to put you in good mood - Best soul / r&b mix ▶ SOUL DEEP COLLECTION 2025
description:
Playlist songs to put you in good mood - Best soul / r&b mix ▶ SOUL DEEP COLLECTION 2025

"This heart knows the ache of absence and the bittersweet pang of memories that flood in during the still moments of the night. Each sob is a note in a melancholic symphony, a testament to the love once held so close, now a haunting melody that plays on repeat. Yet, there is a raw beauty in this suffering, for only a heart that has loved with such abandon can truly understand the stakes of human connection.
This heart sobs not because it is weak, but because it has been strong for too long, bearing the weight of undiluted affection and vulnerability.
In its sobbing, there is a rhythm, a pulse that speaks to the essence of love. It knows that to love is to risk heartbreak, but to withhold love is to deny the essence of existence. Each tear, a mixture of joy and sorrow, is a reminder that to feel so profoundly is the greatest gift of the human experience.
This narrative is not just about the pain of a sobbing heart but about its incredible ability to continue loving, to find renewal in the midst of despair. It is a celebration of the resilience of the human spirit, a confirmation that even in tears, there is a strength that can overcome, heal, and eventually, love again with the same intensity.
Such a heart does not sob in vain. It sobs because it knows the infinite value of love, and through its tears, it teaches us all what it means to love truly, deeply, and without end"

Get your kids moving, having fun, being silly and learning with Danny Go! Tired of YouTube simple nursery rhymes? Every Danny Go! video is packed with original songs for kids and dances for kids that even mom, dad, teachers and caretakers can enjoy! Play freeze games, floor is lava games, this or that games, construction vehicle games and more! title: Jenna Davis - SIKE (Official Music Video)
description:
Jenna Davis - SIKE (Official Music Video) HEY guys it's Jenna Davis! Sit back and enjoy watching the official music video for my newest single "SIKE". This song is the title track to my debut EP "SIKE"! I had always wanted to write a song titled SIKE and one day I brought it into the writing room at Warner Chapel Music in Nashville and in maybe two hours we wrote the whole thing! This song is about when your ex moves on with someone else really quickly and they show him/her off to upset you. It's super sarcastic and definitely more edgy than anything I have done before! A lot of people are saying this is giving them Avril Lavigne vibes...lmk what you think!! I am so incredibly proud of this song & music video! 

🎸 BE THE FIRST TO LISTEN TO "SIKE" (MY NEW EP) here: https://sl.cmdshft.com/sike

american love
american me

as the daylight fell
sangria in a canteen
talking to myself (I can't remember)

this tattoo on my left hand

daydreams of the romance
daydreams of you (you)

my pretty woman in a ballgown
i'm richard gere in a tux
getting married in a courthouse
writing vows in a rush

making out before the judge
with my teenage wife
got a wedding band done
that I just might die with

it's an american wedding
they don't mean too much
but we were so in love
we had an american wedding
now what's mine is yours
that's american law

m-r-s dot kennedy
she signed her name in pen (oh)
in the fancy, fancy cursive (oh)
then turned her term papers in (oh, oh)

a thesis on Islamic (oh)
virgin brides and arranged marriage (ah, ah)
hijabs and polygamist husbands
those poor un-american girls

after school she ran to me
jumped in my 5.0
this is the home of the brave, land of the free
but your parents still didn't know (oh)

she said, "I've had a hell of a summer
so, baby, don't take this hard
but maybe we should get an annulment
before this goes way too far" (oh)

they don't mean too much
they don't last enough

now what's mine is yours
american divorce

well, you can have my Mustang
that's all I've got in my name
but Jesus Christ, don't break my heart
this wedding ring won't ever wipe off

but if you stay
oh, if you stay (stay)
you'll probably leave later, anyway
it''s love made in the USA

description:

#fromamansperspective #dax #manhood #relationships #heartbroken 

LYRICS: 

I thought we forever, 
that’s was a mistake 
you wrote it down pencil, guess it got erased 
Drawing on my weakness, 
look what you create 
A masterpiece of everything 
you taught yourself to hate 
I’m had to log off, your passwords changed 
You always tried to run 
I wasn’t down to chase 
your trauma made you numb 
I tried to give you faith 
you took my kindness and threw it 
right back in my face. 
Ashamed to say I loved you 
and it hurts me cause I actually tried 
your truth was based off of lies. 
Your love was conditional and mine 
forgave you multiple times
That’s why I had to finally walk away 
it hurt me to leave, but was killing me to stay the story of my life This chapter and page is getting ripped out and 
thrown in emotional flames. 
To be honest I don’t hate you 
this my only way to grieve 
what you want isn’t always what you need
I remember days I’d beg and I’d plead 
for you to just calm down 
and provide me with peace 
your words used to hurt me 
they would bring me to my knees 
called me pathetic, trash, weak, 
so I got strong got back on my feet 
picked you up off the sidewalk 
through you back to the streets. 
I don’t want to talk about those times 
that you lied 
don’t wanna talk about 
Those times that I cried 
Don’t want to talk about those times you denied all the truths 
that I spewed that I knew deep inside 
the pressure I was feeling 
that was right up to my neck
The anxiety depression 
that was weighing on my chest 
The constant allegations, 
the blatant disrespect 
the time that I lost, or the money that I spent I was going crazy I was a shell of a man trapped in your cage, lost in your maze Blinded by love addicted to the pain 
the highs and the lows 
the storm and the rain 
I started therapy to cope 
because you drove me insane 
gassed me right up, then emptied my tank, so don’t you try to spin the Block 
when you see I’m doing great 
or that I’m happy 
or I got another woman in your place.
Because I gave you 
too many chances to understand 
That Pain sounds different 
when it’s coming from a man 
we not allowed to feel, be real 
explain, express, and when we do 
we lose the upper hand, 
we only have value 
based on what we can provide. 
I spoke your love language 
you didn’t understand mine 
you pushed me to the edge, 
played like you were blind, 
and then you blamed all of your actions 
on your zodiac sign

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If you made it this deep you're a real one. Thank you for continuing to allow me to use my platform to make an impact. Your support is appreciated more than you'll ever know and I will continue to prove that with my actions. I'm very excited. 2025 is going to bring our best and most impactful work. I am putting everything into creating pieces we can all be proud of. We are the label! Like, comment, SHARE and let's continue to be the change we wish to see in the world. Love you all

Wardruna present the title track of upcoming album Birna, further unraveling the relationship between man and bear. title: 반려견의 깊은 잠을 돕는 12시간 음악🐶🐾강아지를 위한 항불안 음악💖3분 만에 즉각적인 수면🎵
description:
12시간 반려견 깊은 잠을 돕는 음악 🐶🐾 강아지를 위한 항불안 음악 💖 3분 만에 즉각적인 수면 🎵

1. 12시간 연속 음악
12시간 동안 지속되는 음악으로, 강아지가 하루 종일 편안하게 쉴 수 있는 환경을 제공합니다. 지속적인 진정 효과로 깊은 수면을 유도합니다.

2. 강아지 수면 촉진
특별히 설계된 음악은 강아지의 수면을 도와줍니다. 3분 이내에 즉각적인 수면 효과를 경험할 수 있도록 돕습니다.

3. 항불안 음악
강아지의 불안을 줄이고, 스트레스를 완화하는 음악입니다. 혼자 있을 때의 불안과 스트레스를 감소시켜, 더 안정적이고 편안한 상태를 유지할 수 있게 해줍니다.

4. 즉각적인 수면 유도
음악의 편안한 멜로디가 강아지를 빠르게 진정시키고, 수면 상태로 유도합니다. 3분 이내에 효과적인 수면을 경험할 수 있습니다.

5. 편안한 분위기 조성
음악은 강아지의 환경을 평온하게 만들어줍니다. 안정적인 분위기를 조성하여, 강아지가 더 쉽게 잠들 수 있도록 돕습니다.

이 음악을 통해 강아지의 깊은 잠을 촉진하고, 불안을 줄여서 보다 편안한 상태를 유지할 수 있도록 지원하세요.

title: HOW CHARLIE PUTH PRODUCED "LIGHT SWITCH" #charlieputh  #musicproducer
description:
HOW CHARLIE PUTH LIGHT SWITCH WAS PRODUCED

"Light Switch" is a song recorded and produced by American singer-songwriter Charlie Puth. It was released on January 20, 2022, as the lead single from his third studio album, Charlie (2022). Puth wrote the song alongside Jacob Kasher Hindlin and Jake Torrey.A funky, uptempo track, the song lyrically sees Puth crooning about his attraction to a love interest.[1] The song was teased several times on his TikTok account, causing the video to go viral on the platform, with many videos being made using the audio

In November 2021, Puth revealed "a single" would come out in 2022 by responding to a comment on Twitter."Light Switch" then was teased on TikTok that same month, showing him documenting the production of the song. The video went viral on the platform, with a presave for the song made available on November 24, 2021. Throughout the rest of 2021, Puth kept teasing the song in various videos on TikTok. On January 18, 2022, Puth revealed the release date and cover art for "Light Switch" on his social media accounts

Songwriter:Charlie Puth Jacob Kasher Hindlin Jake Torrey
Producer: Charlie Puth @charlieputh

title: 揽佬 SKAI ISYOURGOD—八方来财·因果（Unofficial Extended Music Video）
description:
This fan-made extended music video is non-commercial and created for creative expression under fair use. All credit goes to 揽佬SKAI ISYOURGOD. For concerns, please contact me.

"八方来财·因果" explores the interplay between karma and fate, blending traditional Chinese beliefs with modern themes. Opening with "种瓜得瓜，种豆得豆" ("you reap what you sow"), it emphasizes karma as both a spiritual and scientific reality.

The lyrics depict a dialogue with the divine, seeking blessings for success while cautioning against power struggles. The protagonist is reminded to uphold morality ("老天叮嘱这辈子我善不丢"), reinforcing that virtue attracts divine favor. As wealth grows, so do temptations ("魑魅魍魉" emerge after the harvest), symbolizing the darker side of prosperity. Taking an active stance, the protagonist combats these forces ("我一棍铲除啮齿类"), shaping their own karma.

The recurring question "该不该放下屠刀" ("Should I put down the butcher’s knife?") presents a moral dilemma—continue the struggle or seek redemption? The song ultimately portrays karma as not just fate but a force shaped by personal choices.

description:
እቴ ወይ ልዋል(2)
ከደረትሽ መሀል
  ናፈቀችኝ ጎንደር(2)
 የእነ አሞራው ሀገር
 
  በቅዳሴው ቦታ ቀለሀ ሲዘምር
 እንዴት ሰንብተሻል እናትዋ ጎንደር
 እናትዋ ብልሽ 
ትንፋሽዋ ብልሽ
አካልዋ ብልሽ
መቼ ደረስኩልሽ

ሹርባ ሆኗል ጎፈሬው 
እንደ መይሳው ሊያደርገው
ያ ጎንደሬው
ምነው ገብርየን ቢያረገኝ
አሞራው ውብነህ ቢያረገኝ
ከፊት እንድገኝ

አሞራው ከአሞራ(4)

ያየም ሰው ይናገር የነበረም ያውጋ
ተጋጥሟል ይባላል አሞራው ከአሞራ  
ጎንደር ጀግና ትውለድ ታሳድግ ፀንሳ
እንደአሞራው ውብነህ ስሙ ማይረሳ
ሀገርና እምነቱን ከእራሱ አስበልጦ
ለጠላት ያለቅሳል ውዳሴውን ገልጦ

ጎንደር ጎንደር ደስ ይበልሽ
ደም መላሽ አርበኛው አሞራው መጣልሽ
የሰው ነው የሰው የሰው አመሉ
ማን መጣ ቢሏችሁ ጎንደሬው ነው በሉ

አሞራው ከአሞራ 
  ኢትዬጵያን ሊያገባት አብጠሊሷን ቀዶ
 ልጇ ደረሰላት ሞት ወዶና ፈቅዶ
ወይ አንች እናታለም ወይ አንች መበለት
እንድሜ ብርክ ሲይዘው ልጅ ይሆናል ጎልበት
ወልቃይት ጠገዴ አጅሬ ጃኖራ
ምን አይነት ፍርድ ነው አሞራው ከአሞራ
አሞራው ከአሞራ(3)

ሲሆን መጡ መጡ እንባል ነበረ
እንሂድባቸው ማሸነፍ ካልቀረ
ደሞ ተዚ ተዚህ ተወዲያ ተወዲህ
ጎንደር ከአንች በፊት ያድርገኝ ተንግዲህ
እናትዋ ጎንደር እጅ የዘረጋችው
ዘነበች መሸሻን ወልዳ የሳመችው
ምድር ቀዝቀዝ ሲል ተላይ እያሞቀው
ይኸው ቀብረር ብሎ አሞራው ጠበቀው
አሞራው ጠበቀው

ሀገር እንደዋዛ ናፍቆት እንደዋዛ
የእነ አሞራው ሀገር የመይሳው ካሳ 
አዘዞ ድማዛ
የጃንተከል ዋርካው ወደ መሬት ዘሟል
እንኳን ያደገብሽ ያየሽ በአይኑ ታሟል
እናትዋ ጎንደር

ተይ ደሜ(3)
በላ ልበልሀ እንካንጅ ተቀበል
አሞራው ተነሳ ከእንግዲህ ዝም አትበል
የአለም ፀሀይ እታባ ፊትሽ አይቀየር
የተጠማው በልቶ ለብሶ ጠግቦ ቢያድር
ከተኮሰ ማይስት ጀግና ክንደ ብርቱ
ያ የአርበኛው ምንጣፍ ያ ምጅምር ገጡ
የጦሩ መሳፍንት ፈሪሀ እግዜር ያለው
ከጦር መሀል ሲሄድ ይመስላል ክንፍ ያለው
አሞራው ከአሞራ(8)
አሞራ ምት ለምዶ አካሌ ተቆጣ
ልሂድ ወንድነቴን አሳድሸው ልምጣ
ከዳሽን ላይ ፈልቆ ቀድታ የጠጣችው
የነካትን ሁሉ አቃጥላ ፈጀችው
ከሱዳን ገዳሪፍ ተስቦ እንደ ሰርዶ
ኢትዬጵያን ሰቀላት ያን ሰንደቅ አውርዶ
የአበቅየለሽ ልጆች ዳር እስከዳር ኩሩ
ጎንደር ጀግና አታጣም አትጠራጠሩ(3)
አሞራው ከአሞራ (2)

description:
Gavin Adcock - Need To (Audio)

TOUR DATES: https://www.gavinadcockmusic.com/tour

FOLLOW:
Official Website: https://www.gavinadcockmusic.com
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/gavinadcockmusic
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@gavinadcockmusic 
X: https://twitter.com/gavinadcock

Gavin Adcock is a 25-year-old Georgia native-born and raised in Watkinsville. Former Georgia Southern University football player, Gavin grew up working on his family cattle farm and dreamed of riding bulls in the PBR. He started writing songs in high school, but it wasn’t until the Spring of 2021, when he tore up his knee playing football, that he used his time healing to record and release his first original single. Since then, he has put all focus into his music and has released multiple singles that now have amassed more than hundreds of millions of streams collectively. His recent release, “A Cigarette”, crossed the 30 million streams mark in just a few short months. As he continues to write and record new music, he is hitting the road touring throughout 2024 with sold-out headline dates and multiple major festival plays.

title: Does “Die With A Smile” by Bruno Mars & Lady Gaga Sound Familiar? 🤔🎈#music #brunomars
description:
So, people have noticed that Die With A Smile sounds strangely familiar… 🎶 But here’s the weird part—it might actually be accidental! 

This song uses a clever trick found in viral hits like Bruno Mars' biggest hits like Locked Out of Heaven, and APT. with Rosé.

These songs flip melodies and drum patterns found in, Gotye’s Somebody That I Used to Know, Taylor Swift’s Shake It Off and Avril Lavigne’s Girlfriend. 

And this is a huge part of why Bruno’s songs became instant hits. 

And what’s even crazier is that ‘Die With A Smile’ accidentally shares a melody with the theme from Pixar’s 2009 movie “UP”

Thank you Earthfueled for helping with the edit!

title: RELAXING COUNTRY MUSIC MIX – Best Playlist for a Peaceful Country Escape 🌾💿
description:
🎶 Subscribe now for daily country music! Whether you love classic country legends or today’s modern country hits, we bring you the best country mixes every day. Hit that 🔔 and never miss a song!!

Step into the heart of American country music with this ultimate country mix, featuring soulful vocals that capture the essence of classic and modern country. Whether you’re looking for a top country playlist to unwind, take a road trip across the USA, or find inspiration in heartfelt lyrics, this video brings the warm, nostalgic charm of country music to life.

✨ What to Expect:

🌾 Soulful Vocals – Experience the best of classic and contemporary country, with voices reminiscent of legendary American country artists like Johnny Cash, George Strait, Willie Nelson, Alan Jackson, and Merle Haggard, alongside today’s country stars such as Luke Combs, Morgan Wallen, Chris Stapleton, and Zach Bryan. These heartfelt performances evoke emotions of love, resilience, and small-town life across the United States.

🎸 Timeless Country Soundscapes – Enjoy a mix of acoustic guitars, steel guitar, fiddles, banjos, and smooth harmonies, blending the iconic sounds of the 60s, 70s, 80s, 90s, and today’s country hits. Whether you’re drawn to the storytelling of Hank Williams and Waylon Jennings or the contemporary sounds of Eric Church and Cody Johnson, this playlist delivers a perfect balance of old and new.

🌅 Breathtaking Country Visuals – Immerse yourself in scenic landscapes of wide-open fields, rustic barns, dusty backroads, and golden-hour sunsets. These stunning visuals reflect the beauty of rural America, from the rolling hills of Tennessee to the wide plains of Texas, bringing you closer to the heart of country music.

🐎 A Journey Through Country Music – This extended playlist is ideal for long drives on endless highways, studying, unwinding, or creating a cozy atmosphere. Whether you’re reminiscing about classic American country or enjoying the top country hits of today, this mix is your go-to country escape.

🎵 Perfect For: 
✔ Relaxation & Stress Relief – Let the smooth harmonies and soft country melodies soothe your soul.
✔ Road Trips & Country Drives – The perfect mix for cruising down scenic routes across the USA.
✔ Background Music for Work & Study – Peaceful and inspiring country tunes for focus and creativity.
✔ Southern Nights & Romantic Evenings – The ideal soundtrack for slow dances and candlelit porch nights.
✔ Country Legends & Modern Stars – A nostalgic and fresh blend of classic and new country artists.

description:

Bookings & events:
The Maestro and Wendy Kokkelkoren are available for performances worldwide, including and excluding the Orchestra. Booking information for live;- TV;- or show performances visit the 
website: https://www.themaestro.nl.

—————————————————————

About Guido Dieteren (The Maestro):
Guido Dieteren (1974) is an orchestra leader, violin soloist, arranger and composer. He grew up in a special musical Limburg (The Netherlands) family. Guido's great-grandfather, grandfather and father were all conductors and with it his great musical examples. At an early age, Guido established his name as a concertmaster and soloist of various orchestras and then continued his career as a conductor, violinist and soloist with his own orchestra. Since then, he has played successful concert tours throughout Europe, China and North America.

During his conservatory study in Maastricht, Guido approached his childhood friend and pop keyboard player Falco Borsboom to compose, arrange and work on a new rousing orchestral production. Guido's Orchestra was born (now known as "The Maestro & The European Pop Orchestra")!

Since then, The Maestro & The European Pop Orchestra has experienced many musical highlights. Together with his orchestra, Maestro Guido has provided concerts all over the world, composed and arranged music for commercials (such as McDonald's, Rabobank, WWF, Dela, and AllSecur), played in several international TV shows, released several gold CDs and DVDs, produced large TV specials in all known world languages and performed live for more than 2.7 million visitors. Guido also collaborated as musical director and was involved artistically with many (inter)national artists such as Lionel Richie, Andrea Bocelli, Diana Ross, DJ AfroJack, Simply Red, Caro Emerald, Alessandro Safina, Marco Borsato, Doe Maar, Anouk, Jan Smit, Nick and Simon, Paul de Leeuw and many others.

Guido's heart is not only taken by The Maestro & The European Pop Orchestra and his passion for music. No, he also married the orchestra's solo soprano, Wendy Kokkelkoren, in 2006. After the first concert together, the spark caught on and since then, they have been inseparable. Together with their daughters Emma-Sophie and Annabel, Guido and Wendy form a happy musical family.

Artistic wishlist in the coming years, new TV Specials and songs will be recorded. The Maestro & The European Pop Orchestra wants to perform in many countries, like: United States, the Netherlands, United Kingdom, Belgium, Spain, Germany, Portugal, Poland, France, Italy, Brazil, South Korea, Philippines, China, Japan, Taiwan. 

Please spread the word to family and friends! Make some advertisement for The Maestro & The European Pop Orchestra, and we will be soon performing in your beautiful country!

description:
A Ruben's tube is a physics apparatus for demonstrating acoustic standing waves in a tube. Invented by German physicist Heinrich Rubens in 1905, it graphically shows the relationship between sound waves and sound pressure. In this video a trumpet player is using the Ruben's tube to visualize the sound of a trumpet.

Video Courtesy @moises.alves.73

title: Melar Gaan (মেলার গান)​⁠​⁠|@HooliGaanism|Music Video 2025|Anirban,Subhadeep,Debraj|Riddhi|SVF Music
description:
ঘুরছে চাকা, ঘুরছে সময়, ঘুরছে নাগরদোলা। দু'দিনের যন্ত্র জীবনে বাহারি রঙ ভরে দেয় বকুলতলার মেলা। সেই মেলার nostalgia এবার নতুনভাবে ধরা পড়ল Hooligaanism-এর গানে... শুনে নিন অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্যের কথায়, দেবরাজ ভট্টাচার্য, শুভদীপ গুহ ও অনির্বাণ ভট্টাচার্যের সুরে #Hooligaanism ব্যান্ডের গাওয়া 'মেলার গান' শুধুমাত্র ​⁠@SVFMusic  -এ।

The wheel spins, time moves, and the Ferris wheel keeps turning. In the mechanical rhythm of life, Bakultala Mela fills the days with vibrant colors. Now nostalgia comes alive in a new way through Hooliganism’s song. Listen to 'Melar Gaan', written by Anirban Bhattacharya, composed and sung by Debraj Bhattacharya, Subhadeep Guha, and Anirban Bhattacharya, exclusively on ​⁠@SVFMusic.

#Hooligaanism #MelarGaan #SVFMusic

title: What is music streaming fraud and how rampant is it?  - BBC Trending podcast, BBC World Service
description:
In September last year, musician Mike Smith of North Carolina was charged with stealing millions from music streaming services. 

Click here to subscribe to our channel 👉🏽 https://bbc.in/3VyyriM

The US Department of Justice has accused him of using artificial intelligence tools and thousands of bots to fraudulently stream songs billions of times - taking millions of dollars of royalties which otherwise would have been paid to real artists.

Smith isn’t just a regular amateur musician. He’s collaborated with some huge artists – including Snoop Dogg, DJ Khaled and Billy Ray Cyrus. He’s also starred as a judge on One Shot, a hip-hop reality TV programme on the cable network BET (Black Entertainment Television). We speak to Jonathan Hay, a celebrity publicist and producer who says he was the first person to report Smith to the FBI, and from another colleague of Smith’s who has a very different view of the man. 

The case has been labeled as ‘unprecedented’ and ‘the first of its kind’ in the press. We explore whether fraud on music streaming services actually be much more prevalent than any of the platforms let on.

00:00 Introduction
00:15 The case - who is Mike Smith and what is he accused of?
01:05 How does getting paid from music streaming work?
02:52 Jonathan Hay interview - the man who reported his partner for music streaming fraud
05:44 Goldy Locks interview - who questions if streaming fraud is a big deal
07:32 Andrew Batey interview - how the Mike Smith case can impact music streaming
08:22 So what now?

Reporter/Producer: Beth Godwin
Producer/Director: Omar Mehtab
Film Editor: Carel Nell
Executive Producer/Editor: Flora Carmichael
Senior Editor: Finlo Rohrer

description:
We are excited to bring you an exquisite blend of Arab oud melodies and Flamenco rumba rhythms! This music captures the soulful essence of North African, Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, and Spanish-inspired guitar instrumentals. Perfect for relaxation, focus, reading, or even meditation, these serene tunes highlight the captivating sounds of the oud, guitar, and gentle percussion. Let the ethereal vibes take you on a journey through Moroccan allure, Spanish elegance, and Mediterranean serenity.

title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

description:
Get ready for something truly unique in "Ranking The Best Phonk With Violin Cover"!
